WEBVTT

00:12.030 --> 00:13.960
Although the Seventh Prince
is at the border,

00:13.960 --> 00:16.190
he has always been concerned
about your health, Your Highness.

00:16.190 --> 00:17.390
These are the border specialties

00:17.390 --> 00:19.160
that His Highness had people prepare.

00:19.160 --> 00:20.870
Hongteng fruit and mistletoe—

00:20.870 --> 00:22.920
they are foods beneficial to the fetus.

00:22.920 --> 00:25.120
He specifically asked me,
upon returning to the capital,

00:25.120 --> 00:26.250
to bring them to you.

00:28.230 --> 00:30.070
The physician warned me

00:30.440 --> 00:32.600
not to eat food of unknown origin.

00:33.030 --> 00:36.280
There are too many things to dispose of
in my mansion every day

00:36.280 --> 00:37.790
You should take these things

00:37.790 --> 00:39.190
back exactly as they are.

00:39.200 --> 00:39.880
Your Highness,

00:39.880 --> 00:41.560
this is a token
of the Seventh Prince's affection.

00:41.560 --> 00:41.960
You...

00:41.980 --> 00:44.040
I think too much during my pregnancy.

00:44.350 --> 00:45.810
If you truly care about me,

00:46.110 --> 00:47.510
don't come here anymore.

00:48.750 --> 00:49.750
See the guest out.

00:51.200 --> 00:52.330
I will take my leave.

00:59.240 --> 01:01.070
I know a little bit about medicine.

01:01.070 --> 01:02.390
The things the Seventh Prince sent

01:02.390 --> 01:03.960
are indeed good things.

01:04.310 --> 01:06.710
Why didn't you accept them, Your Highness?

01:08.230 --> 01:09.400
Zhao Che

01:09.400 --> 01:10.950
is now a hidden threat to my father

01:10.950 --> 01:13.230
and the Thirteenth Prince.

01:13.950 --> 01:16.410
Since I belong to
the Thirteenth Prince now,

01:16.710 --> 01:19.240
I naturally have to draw a clear line
with him.

01:19.510 --> 01:20.070
Go.

01:21.070 --> 01:23.330
Light the incense left by Jia Meng for me.

01:23.760 --> 01:24.400
Yes.

02:16.680 --> 02:17.360
Li Yan,

02:18.560 --> 02:19.360
you're here?

02:21.150 --> 02:22.079
You know what?

02:23.360 --> 02:26.030
I will soon
be the Princess Protector of the State.

02:26.030 --> 02:27.630
I will be more noble

02:27.630 --> 02:29.120
than ever before.

02:29.870 --> 02:31.730
What you couldn't give our child,

02:32.960 --> 02:34.620
I will make it up to him double.

04:25.330 --> 04:30.730
[REBIRTH]

04:31.680 --> 04:33.790
[Episode 30]

04:37.190 --> 04:39.720
Faceless God, please grant me strength,

04:40.870 --> 04:43.360
let Great Yong and Great Yan fight again,

04:44.190 --> 04:46.560
and make sure Zhao Che dies at the border!

05:22.680 --> 05:25.270
The Faceless God has granted your wish.

05:25.600 --> 05:26.240
Really?

05:27.160 --> 05:27.720
Yes.

05:28.360 --> 05:30.360
I have more good news for you.

05:31.160 --> 05:33.620
Jia Meng has already taken action
in Ximeng.

05:33.800 --> 05:35.430
The land and black gold mines of Ximeng

05:35.430 --> 05:36.690
will all belong to you.

05:36.830 --> 05:38.920
By then, even if Zhao Che doesn't die,

05:39.390 --> 05:41.850
Father won't even
spare him another glance.

05:41.870 --> 05:43.430
You will become

05:43.800 --> 05:46.000
the only heir to the throne in his heart.

05:53.630 --> 05:55.390
After I take over Ximeng,

05:55.560 --> 05:57.070
I'll ask Father

05:57.680 --> 05:59.070
to kill Zhao Che!

05:59.390 --> 06:01.040
Isn't he just good at fighting wars?

06:01.040 --> 06:03.600
Father will no longer need him by then.

06:04.040 --> 06:06.750
And Great Yong
will no longer need him either!

06:13.870 --> 06:14.830
Sister Chun.

06:19.240 --> 06:21.040
If I become the Crown Prince,

06:23.480 --> 06:25.830
I will make you
the Princess Protector of the State.

06:25.830 --> 06:28.120
I want everyone to crawl at your feet,

06:28.120 --> 06:29.380
look up to your beauty,

06:30.870 --> 06:31.920
worship you,

06:32.680 --> 06:33.720
and submit to you.

06:35.270 --> 06:36.270
What do you think?

06:46.040 --> 06:46.870
These...

06:47.000 --> 06:49.560
are probably the names of the brothers
still in Qingshan Manor.

06:49.560 --> 06:50.630
After you left,

06:50.630 --> 06:53.270
Qingshan Manor
dealt with a group of Moon Guards.

06:53.270 --> 06:55.670
Some brothers wanted to escape to survive,

06:56.040 --> 06:56.720
but...

06:56.800 --> 06:57.510
But...

06:58.680 --> 07:01.810
they were all dealt with
by my grandfather and Lord Zhan.

07:02.000 --> 07:02.680
Right?

07:04.800 --> 07:06.600
Once a person of Qingshan Manor,

07:06.870 --> 07:08.800
always a person of Qingshan Manor.

07:09.000 --> 07:10.480
This is the rule of Qingshan Manor.

07:10.480 --> 07:11.880
What are you doing there?

07:16.160 --> 07:17.290
What are you hiding?

07:17.750 --> 07:18.510
Nothing.

07:27.190 --> 07:29.360
Yue Yong, Yue Zeng?

07:31.360 --> 07:32.470
What is this list?

07:33.510 --> 07:35.600
These are the names
Young Master chose for the child.

07:35.600 --> 07:36.190
Shiyi!

07:37.680 --> 07:38.680
What child?

07:38.920 --> 07:40.190
These are some names
Young Master asked me to look up

07:40.190 --> 07:41.310
and search for.

07:42.040 --> 07:44.840
He said they are options
for your future children.

07:45.430 --> 07:46.120
Yue Shiyi,

07:46.390 --> 07:47.560
what nonsense are you talking about?

07:47.560 --> 07:48.360
Young Master,

07:48.560 --> 07:49.390
don't be shy.

07:49.680 --> 07:51.120
If we don't tell Lady Chu,

07:51.190 --> 07:52.920
you won't be able to explain it.

07:53.040 --> 07:54.560
Why do I feel something's off?

07:54.560 --> 07:55.630
Most of the names

07:55.870 --> 07:57.680
on this list are male.

07:57.750 --> 07:58.950
There is a female name.

07:58.950 --> 07:59.560
Look,

07:59.720 --> 08:01.510
this is the one the Young Master picked.

08:01.510 --> 08:02.160
Yuegui?

08:02.430 --> 08:03.000
Right.

08:03.600 --> 08:04.560
The Young Master likes

08:04.560 --> 08:05.960
the name Yuegui the most.

08:06.190 --> 08:08.680
He hopes you will be together forever

08:08.680 --> 08:09.750
and have children soon.

08:09.750 --> 08:10.360
Shiyi!

08:16.310 --> 08:17.570
Let's go out for a walk.

08:25.010 --> 08:29.640
[Chu's Mansion]

08:41.909 --> 08:42.909
It is this tree.

08:49.480 --> 08:50.360
Yuegui

08:50.750 --> 08:52.080
is the name of this tree?

08:52.910 --> 08:53.970
Not a child's name?

08:55.000 --> 08:57.000
This kind of tree cannot be seen

08:57.000 --> 08:57.870
in Great Yong and Biantang.

08:57.870 --> 08:59.870
It can only grow in Ximeng

08:59.870 --> 09:01.600
and the continent further west.

09:01.600 --> 09:02.910
It may be slender now,

09:03.440 --> 09:04.440
but in a few years,

09:04.630 --> 09:06.750
it will be big enough
to shade the whole yard.

09:06.750 --> 09:08.550
We can enjoy the shade in summer.

09:09.030 --> 09:10.630
It will bloom in autumn,

09:10.960 --> 09:13.490
and the fragrance
of laurel will fill the air.

09:14.910 --> 09:16.870
When Ximeng is at peace again

09:17.200 --> 09:18.600
and we finally have time,

09:18.600 --> 09:21.550
we can enjoy tea and flowers
under this tree

09:22.790 --> 09:23.720
and eat hot pot.

09:27.440 --> 09:28.360
You just said

09:28.630 --> 09:30.360
Yuegui is the name of this tree.

09:30.480 --> 09:32.630
Then what are Yue Yong and Yue Zeng?

09:36.670 --> 09:37.480
They wouldn't

09:37.910 --> 09:39.910
really be children's names, right?

09:57.780 --> 09:59.040
What's wrong with you?

10:02.440 --> 10:03.600
I never thought

10:05.050 --> 10:07.110
I would spend a day like this with you.

10:28.270 --> 10:30.320
I made a plate of pastries today—
a rather rare thing for me.

10:30.320 --> 10:30.780
Come on.

10:31.080 --> 10:31.960
Try some.

10:38.870 --> 10:40.670
How are they? Do they taste good?

10:42.080 --> 10:43.150
Yes.

10:43.150 --> 10:43.870
Taste good.

10:45.030 --> 10:45.750
Taste good.

10:46.670 --> 10:47.550
Taste good.

10:50.750 --> 10:51.350
Well...

10:52.200 --> 10:53.030
Lady Chu,

10:53.240 --> 10:54.790
it's your first time making pastries.

10:54.790 --> 10:55.720
It's normal

10:56.510 --> 10:57.710
for them to taste bad.

10:57.720 --> 10:59.030
It's not my first time.

10:59.360 --> 11:00.240
Before in Qingshan Manor,

11:00.240 --> 11:01.670
when I made them for Zhuge Yue,

11:01.670 --> 11:03.000
they were like this too.

11:03.630 --> 11:04.390
Ask him.

11:04.750 --> 11:05.480
Is it good?

11:17.670 --> 11:18.320
Yes.

11:35.150 --> 11:36.610
It's the fruit's problem.

11:42.910 --> 11:43.440
No.

11:44.270 --> 11:45.870
The fruit is sour and bitter.

11:46.150 --> 11:47.080
What's going on?

11:47.200 --> 11:48.550
I heard from the kitchen

11:48.790 --> 11:50.000
that recently,
the sour fruit trees in Ximeng

11:50.000 --> 11:51.800
have caught a strange epidemic.

11:52.150 --> 11:54.080
So the palace stopped buying them.

11:54.440 --> 11:55.700
This is the last batch.

11:55.870 --> 11:56.790
It seems

11:57.080 --> 11:58.880
this batch can't be used either.

11:59.360 --> 12:00.200
Epidemic?

12:07.080 --> 12:08.200
Excuse me!

12:09.150 --> 12:09.870
What happened?

12:09.870 --> 12:11.170
The road ahead is blocked.

12:11.170 --> 12:13.150
These people are gathering
in the center of the city,

12:13.150 --> 12:14.680
asking for some holy water.

12:16.150 --> 12:17.120
It seems

12:17.320 --> 12:18.270
our carriage

12:18.270 --> 12:19.930
can't get through for a while.

12:23.720 --> 12:24.750
Let's split up.

12:24.870 --> 12:27.200
You and Xiao Ran go to the orchard
outside the city.

12:27.200 --> 12:29.460
I'll go over there and see what happened.

12:47.240 --> 12:48.870
Look at these sand date trees.

12:48.870 --> 12:50.030
The infected ones

12:50.480 --> 12:51.680
are rotting all over.

12:53.200 --> 12:54.460
How could this happen?

12:55.870 --> 12:57.200
And the color of the soil

12:57.320 --> 12:58.270
is a bit strange.

12:58.480 --> 13:00.080
The soil in Ximeng is mostly red,

13:00.080 --> 13:01.280
but look at this soil—

13:01.750 --> 13:02.680
it's a bit green.

13:05.790 --> 13:08.270
Up ahead, it should be
the water source for this orchard.

13:08.270 --> 13:09.600
Let's go and take a look.

13:13.270 --> 13:14.240
Don't you think

13:14.550 --> 13:16.750
these birds and beasts died strangely?

13:19.870 --> 13:21.730
The river is obviously polluted.

13:21.840 --> 13:22.790
This seems to be

13:23.600 --> 13:24.930
some kind of sacrifice.

13:32.620 --> 13:33.550
It's time for the holy water.

13:33.550 --> 13:34.200
Sir.

13:34.790 --> 13:35.390
Sir,

13:35.390 --> 13:37.630
what are you going to get?

13:37.630 --> 13:39.090
The holy water, of course.

13:39.720 --> 13:40.580
The holy water?

13:41.120 --> 13:42.180
What is holy water?

13:42.200 --> 13:44.080
The holy water is a cure-all.

13:44.150 --> 13:46.080
As long as we believe in the Saintess
devoutly,

13:46.080 --> 13:47.600
she will give us holy water.

13:47.600 --> 13:50.000
I heard it can also cure
the crabapple trees' disease.

13:50.000 --> 13:51.630
Stop talking. Let's go!

13:51.630 --> 13:54.290
There won't be any holy water left
if we're late.

13:55.120 --> 13:56.320
Thank you. Thank you.

13:58.720 --> 14:00.030
And me!

14:00.140 --> 14:00.570
Me!

14:00.600 --> 14:01.290
Lady Chu,

14:01.630 --> 14:03.120
I'll go ahead and take a look.

14:03.120 --> 14:04.150
Don't push. Come on.

14:04.150 --> 14:05.550
There's one more bottle.

14:11.670 --> 14:12.440
Please!

14:12.840 --> 14:13.700
I want some too!

14:14.510 --> 14:15.000
Me too!

14:15.000 --> 14:15.750
Thank you.

14:40.390 --> 14:41.390
I got it!

14:42.600 --> 14:44.730
Lady Chu, you're looking for someone?

14:45.270 --> 14:46.000
Nothing.

14:46.270 --> 14:47.200
What did you get?

14:48.960 --> 14:51.480
It seems that the crabapple trees outside
the city have got a strange disease.

14:51.480 --> 14:53.140
This holy water can cure them.

14:58.030 --> 14:59.480
I heard from those people

14:59.540 --> 15:00.450
that this Saintess

15:00.450 --> 15:02.250
was chosen by some Faceless God.

15:02.960 --> 15:06.090
And this holy water is also bestowed
by the Faceless God.

15:14.000 --> 15:14.750
I got it.

15:15.600 --> 15:16.200
This is a panacea

15:16.200 --> 15:17.840
called Kuji Grass.

15:17.840 --> 15:19.320
It can cure many common poisons.

15:19.320 --> 15:20.550
If I'm not mistaken,

15:20.550 --> 15:22.120
the water source near the orchard
has been polluted,

15:22.120 --> 15:22.600
and this medicine

15:22.600 --> 15:24.000
is used to detoxify the water.

15:24.000 --> 15:25.080
So the river water

15:25.510 --> 15:26.310
was poisoned?

15:27.240 --> 15:28.000
It should be,

15:28.370 --> 15:30.080
but it's probably not a fatal poison.

15:30.080 --> 15:32.240
The people also drink the river water,
but they are fine.

15:32.240 --> 15:34.080
Only some livestock and fruit trees
were affected.

15:34.080 --> 15:35.940
What exactly is the Faceless God?

15:35.960 --> 15:36.960
Does anyone know?

15:41.040 --> 15:42.430
Faceless God?

15:44.510 --> 15:45.600
Back in the day,

15:45.790 --> 15:47.750
I, Wang Shi'er, went to
the southern and western regions

15:47.750 --> 15:48.840
to rob tombs.

15:49.630 --> 15:51.120
But how come I have never heard

15:51.120 --> 15:52.580
of this god without a face?

15:54.080 --> 15:55.210
Young Master Zhuge.

15:55.550 --> 15:56.510
What happened?

15:56.790 --> 15:58.320
Great Yan has sent a visiting card,

15:58.320 --> 16:00.510
saying the King of Great Yan is coming
to Ximeng to offer congratulations.

16:00.510 --> 16:02.510
He is already outside Ximengcheng.

16:02.630 --> 16:05.490
He will enter the city tomorrow
to pay his respects.

16:06.790 --> 16:07.250
[We are pleased to hear of the promulgation of Ximeng's new policy,
which reforms the old and introduces the new.]

16:07.250 --> 16:07.720
[With wise strategy guiding the state and benevolent governance
benefiting the people, this is truly a blessing for Ximeng and its citizens.]

16:07.740 --> 16:08.240
[Great Yan and Ximeng have long shared cordial relations.
We now wish to partake in your virtuous transformation and contribute to this grand endeavor.]

16:08.240 --> 16:08.750
[We have sent our sincere congratulations along with a modest token
of goodwill, humbly hoping you will accept it.]

16:08.780 --> 16:09.250
[May Ximeng's national fortune endure for generations,]

16:09.250 --> 16:09.720
[and may Your Majesty and the Queen enjoy peace, health, and prosperity.
Yan Xun, King of Great Yan, respectfully bows in salute.]

16:39.910 --> 16:41.550
Congratulations, King and Queen Ximeng,

16:41.550 --> 16:42.910
on your new policy.

16:43.750 --> 16:45.210
My arrival is a bit abrupt.

16:45.240 --> 16:47.240
Please don't take offense.

16:49.240 --> 16:50.720
King of Great Yan,
you have come a long way

16:50.720 --> 16:52.550
to congratulate the Queen and me.

16:52.550 --> 16:54.350
Of course we won't take offense.

16:55.360 --> 16:56.670
However, King of Great Yan,

16:56.670 --> 17:00.330
next time you should send someone
with a visiting card in advance,

17:00.510 --> 17:01.710
so that the Queen and I

17:02.200 --> 17:04.000
can prepare a proper reception.

17:05.480 --> 17:06.200
No need.

17:07.069 --> 17:09.400
I brought some gifts for Queen Ximeng.

17:10.480 --> 17:11.109
Chu.

17:12.030 --> 17:13.760
This is black jade from the peak

17:14.000 --> 17:15.599
of Mount Huihui in Great Yan.

17:15.880 --> 17:17.720
It was formed by the hot springs
at the foot of Mount Huihui

17:17.720 --> 17:19.680
washing over it for hundreds of years.

17:19.680 --> 17:21.200
It can be used to make an imperial seal.

17:21.200 --> 17:22.109
I brought it

17:22.550 --> 17:23.680
to congratulate you

17:24.000 --> 17:25.550
for finally realizing your long-held wish

17:25.550 --> 17:27.950
of freeing the slaves
and stopping the war.

17:30.960 --> 17:31.680
This

17:36.350 --> 17:38.510
is the finest white fox fur
from Great Yan.

17:38.510 --> 17:40.750
The Snowy Region Tribe of Great Yan
guards the northern border.

17:40.750 --> 17:42.160
The weather there is extremely cold.

17:42.160 --> 17:43.880
They have been using animal fur
to make coats

17:43.880 --> 17:45.350
for warmth since ancient times.

17:45.350 --> 17:47.000
But only the leader of the tribe

17:47.000 --> 17:48.830
is entitled to use the white fox fur.

17:48.830 --> 17:50.560
Ximeng has long, harsh winters

17:50.590 --> 17:52.320
that can last up to 5 or 6 months.

17:52.550 --> 17:53.510
These furs

17:54.350 --> 17:56.750
are enough to last you
for several winters.

18:00.110 --> 18:02.310
This is a dust-gold armor from Great Yan.

18:02.310 --> 18:03.270
It looks soft,

18:03.510 --> 18:05.000
but it is invulnerable to all weapons.

18:05.000 --> 18:07.660
It is perfect for you
to wear on the battlefield.

18:08.790 --> 18:10.550
This is blood lingzhi from Great Yan.

18:10.550 --> 18:12.880
It can cure all diseases and prolong life.

18:15.070 --> 18:15.750
Chu.

18:20.090 --> 18:21.290
There is one more gift

18:22.000 --> 18:24.200
that I sent to the horse ranch of Ximeng.

18:24.510 --> 18:25.160
Chu,

18:25.350 --> 18:26.310
I promised you

18:26.360 --> 18:29.560
that I would take you to see
the Huolei horses on Mount Huihui.

18:29.560 --> 18:31.160
I picked 50 of them this time,

18:31.550 --> 18:32.510
all the finest from Great Yan...

18:32.510 --> 18:33.160
Yan Xun.

18:34.790 --> 18:35.550
Come with me.

18:36.350 --> 18:38.410
I have something to talk to you about.

19:04.000 --> 19:04.720
Yan Xun.

19:05.870 --> 19:06.630
How is...

19:08.030 --> 19:09.430
everything in Great Yan?

19:09.750 --> 19:11.480
Everything is fine, of course.

19:15.240 --> 19:16.830
In the battle of Longyin Pass,

19:16.830 --> 19:18.510
Great Yan suffered heavy losses

19:18.510 --> 19:20.040
and was severely weakened.

19:20.070 --> 19:21.790
It's already a bitterly cold place.

19:21.790 --> 19:23.120
Over the past two years,

19:23.200 --> 19:24.830
the people
have been exhausted from military service.

19:24.830 --> 19:25.920
I'm afraid they can no longer bear

19:25.920 --> 19:27.790
any more extortionate taxes and levies.

19:27.790 --> 19:30.030
Your treasury's situation can't be good.

19:30.030 --> 19:31.750
Plus, with the disastrous defeat
of Great Yan,

19:31.750 --> 19:32.590
what you lost

19:32.830 --> 19:35.270
was not only your Black Eagle Army,

19:35.790 --> 19:37.240
but also the Great Yan army

19:37.240 --> 19:39.040
recruited from various tribes.

19:39.160 --> 19:40.070
Nowadays,

19:40.550 --> 19:41.880
the tribe elders of Great Yan

19:41.880 --> 19:43.610
must be complaining about you.

19:43.920 --> 19:45.480
If you are even slightly careless,

19:45.480 --> 19:46.940
they may turn against you.

19:48.000 --> 19:48.830
Right?

19:49.720 --> 19:50.750
You're right.

19:52.200 --> 19:53.400
So my trip here

19:54.110 --> 19:56.040
is to form an alliance with Ximeng.

19:56.070 --> 19:58.070
Whether what you said is true or not,

19:58.350 --> 20:00.080
you should know better than I do

20:00.480 --> 20:02.880
that Great Yan is now facing both
internal turmoil and external threats.

20:02.880 --> 20:04.210
An alliance with Ximeng

20:04.720 --> 20:06.550
is the only and best option.

20:07.830 --> 20:08.720
I used to

20:10.160 --> 20:12.310
regard Great Yan as my hometown

20:12.880 --> 20:15.550
and treat you and the people of Great Yan

20:16.230 --> 20:17.680
as my family.

20:19.960 --> 20:21.760
If you still have any sense left,

20:22.750 --> 20:24.510
you should do as you said.

20:24.960 --> 20:25.720
Let's not

20:25.990 --> 20:27.450
talk about anything else.

20:35.750 --> 20:37.200
They hugged!

20:37.280 --> 20:38.720
They actually hugged?

20:38.790 --> 20:40.160
This is too much.

20:40.180 --> 20:41.960
Isn't this bullying our Young Master?

20:41.960 --> 20:42.790
Yan Xun!

20:49.730 --> 20:50.530
I'm sorry.

20:51.390 --> 20:52.520
I lost my composure.

21:02.440 --> 21:03.240
King Ximeng,

21:03.880 --> 21:05.790
the Queen and I were catching up

21:06.030 --> 21:07.430
and talked a bit too much.

21:07.640 --> 21:08.790
I hope you

21:08.960 --> 21:10.220
will not take offense.

21:15.750 --> 21:16.440
Xing,

21:17.110 --> 21:18.920
the palace is having
the bluestone paths repaired today.

21:18.920 --> 21:19.920
It's hard to walk.

21:20.470 --> 21:21.670
Let me carry you back.

21:32.070 --> 21:33.530
And now he's carrying her?

21:34.510 --> 21:35.590
Young Master won!

22:02.640 --> 22:03.790
Are you jealous?

22:05.000 --> 22:06.330
It is only natural for me

22:06.640 --> 22:07.790
to carry my queen.

22:08.640 --> 22:09.440
Take a guess—

22:09.960 --> 22:11.720
why did Yan Xun come to Ximeng?

22:12.720 --> 22:15.590
Great Yan suffered heavy losses
in the battle with Biantang.

22:15.590 --> 22:16.880
The unity of Great Yan

22:16.880 --> 22:18.880
was maintained by Yan Xun's sheer force.

22:18.880 --> 22:20.160
After all this turmoil,

22:20.160 --> 22:21.590
I'm afraid their internal affairs
have become unstable.

22:21.590 --> 22:23.350
On top of that, with Great Yong
posing an external threat,

22:23.350 --> 22:24.270
I think

22:24.750 --> 22:26.000
he came to Ximeng this time

22:26.000 --> 22:28.030
to seek an alliance

22:28.160 --> 22:30.290
in order to ease pressure on Great Yan.

22:32.200 --> 22:33.460
We think alike on this.

22:33.920 --> 22:34.920
It's just that...

22:35.750 --> 22:36.680
What?

22:36.830 --> 22:38.270
Yan Xun's true purpose

22:38.720 --> 22:40.180
shouldn't be that simple.

22:43.320 --> 22:44.050
Here you are.

22:44.750 --> 22:45.680
Enjoy your meal.

22:46.070 --> 22:46.640
Waiter!

22:46.870 --> 22:47.480
Officers.

22:47.480 --> 22:48.080
The usual.

22:48.270 --> 22:49.200
Coming right up!

22:54.270 --> 22:55.670
Did you see the document?

22:55.750 --> 22:56.950
What does it say, bro?

22:57.510 --> 22:59.400
They found another new mine.

22:59.720 --> 23:01.170
North of Mount Heihe,

23:01.400 --> 23:03.590
the entire mountain range
will be sealed off.

23:03.590 --> 23:04.750
This is huge.

23:05.200 --> 23:05.880
Now,

23:06.510 --> 23:07.680
we will have to

23:07.680 --> 23:09.080
be busy for a while again.

23:09.160 --> 23:10.290
Here are the dishes!

23:12.350 --> 23:13.070
Officers.

23:13.640 --> 23:14.160
Enjoy.

23:15.070 --> 23:16.000
Wine for sale!

23:18.110 --> 23:19.110
Officers.

23:19.960 --> 23:21.590
My caravan and I are new here.

23:21.670 --> 23:23.830
We were planning
to pass through Mount Heihe

23:23.830 --> 23:25.560
to do tea business in the south,

23:25.590 --> 23:27.240
but we found the road blocked.

23:27.240 --> 23:29.550
We happened to hear you mention this,

23:29.790 --> 23:31.190
so we came to ask about it.

23:33.110 --> 23:34.000
Well...

23:36.550 --> 23:39.790
This money is for you to buy some drinks.

23:40.160 --> 23:42.240
Please show us a clear path.

23:43.480 --> 23:44.510
Miss,

23:45.110 --> 23:47.160
you're obviously not a local.

23:48.550 --> 23:51.160
They're mining in Mount Heihe recently.

23:51.680 --> 23:54.000
The main road is definitely impassable.

23:56.270 --> 23:57.510
This puts us in a difficult position.

23:57.510 --> 23:59.000
If we can't go through Mount Heihe,

23:59.000 --> 24:01.000
we'll have to detour at least 100 li.

24:01.270 --> 24:03.000
If the goods are delayed,

24:03.110 --> 24:04.640
we will be stuck with them.

24:06.070 --> 24:06.680
Miss,

24:06.680 --> 24:08.400
don't worry about that.

24:08.640 --> 24:10.200
Although the main road is blocked,

24:10.200 --> 24:12.310
aren't there small paths?

24:12.720 --> 24:15.310
You're lucky you met

24:15.310 --> 24:16.570
us two officers today.

24:16.590 --> 24:17.640
For ordinary people,

24:17.640 --> 24:20.240
it's not so easy to find a way

24:20.240 --> 24:21.510
into the mountain.

24:22.720 --> 24:24.920
There have always been

24:24.920 --> 24:26.960
a few paths in the mountains
used by hunters.

24:26.960 --> 24:29.350
A large group
definitely couldn't get through,

24:29.350 --> 24:32.240
but for a caravan like yours,

24:33.000 --> 24:34.790
it's absolutely no problem.

24:36.000 --> 24:36.920
That's great.

24:37.480 --> 24:39.080
Could you please show us here

24:40.830 --> 24:42.680
which path we should take?

24:45.140 --> 24:46.050
This road

24:46.480 --> 24:48.240
is definitely a dead end.

24:49.020 --> 24:51.910
But this one...

24:57.750 --> 25:00.210
Thank you for solving my problem,
officers.

25:00.400 --> 25:01.070
Miss.

25:03.160 --> 25:04.720
Don't leave in a hurry.

25:04.830 --> 25:05.720
Right.

25:05.720 --> 25:09.310
May I know... how old you are?

25:15.160 --> 25:16.200
Spare me, sir.

25:16.920 --> 25:19.440
I didn't know she was already taken.

25:19.880 --> 25:20.790
It's a misunderstanding.

25:20.790 --> 25:21.320
Get lost!

25:24.160 --> 25:25.550
Bro, wait for me!

25:38.680 --> 25:39.480
Your Majesty.

25:40.070 --> 25:42.590
Although the black gold mine
is adjacent to Great Yan,

25:42.590 --> 25:44.750
within a distance of under 200 miles

25:44.960 --> 25:48.110
lie the Mount Ximin range
and the Blackwater River Valley.

25:48.110 --> 25:49.710
The terrain is treacherous.

25:49.880 --> 25:50.720
Only if we

25:51.110 --> 25:52.440
take a small group of men

25:52.750 --> 25:54.680
to detour through Ximeng territory,

25:54.680 --> 25:56.350
can we quietly

25:56.550 --> 25:57.950
seize the mine entrance.

25:58.640 --> 26:00.570
Detour through Ximeng territory?

26:06.240 --> 26:08.310
I heard from the Ximeng soldiers

26:08.310 --> 26:10.310
heading to mine in Mount Ximin today

26:10.590 --> 26:11.850
that although the area

26:12.030 --> 26:14.200
around the mine is a vast wilderness,

26:14.590 --> 26:17.320
local hunters
often go into the mountains to hunt

26:17.350 --> 26:19.920
and have discovered
several hidden paths in and out.

26:19.920 --> 26:22.450
As long as our men
are divided into small teams

26:22.750 --> 26:24.160
and successively sneak into
these small paths

26:24.160 --> 26:25.890
from within Ximeng territory,

26:26.110 --> 26:28.510
we can enter the hinterland
of Mount Heihe.

26:32.150 --> 26:33.810
The hinterland of Mount Heihe

26:34.110 --> 26:36.440
is not only difficult
for the Great Yan Army to enter,

26:36.440 --> 26:38.750
but also for the Ximeng Army.

26:40.000 --> 26:41.660
As long as we move fast enough,

26:42.310 --> 26:44.310
we can catch them off guard

26:45.070 --> 26:46.310
and seize the black gold mine.

26:46.310 --> 26:47.200
Pass my order.

26:47.680 --> 26:50.110
Have Jing
lead 2,000 Black Eagle Army soldiers

26:50.110 --> 26:51.970
to detour into Ximeng territory.

26:53.200 --> 26:53.960
So soon?

26:54.110 --> 26:55.970
Based on my understanding of Chu,

26:56.000 --> 26:57.200
she definitely won't believe

26:57.200 --> 26:58.590
my reason for coming this time.

26:58.590 --> 26:59.830
The longer we delay,

27:00.200 --> 27:02.130
the more prepared she and Zhuge Yue

27:02.240 --> 27:03.720
will be.

27:04.830 --> 27:05.350
Yes.

27:15.640 --> 27:16.310
Chu,

27:16.920 --> 27:17.960
don't blame me.

27:18.350 --> 27:19.510
You said it yourself

27:19.960 --> 27:22.020
that Great Yan was also once your home

27:22.270 --> 27:25.640
and the people of Great Yan
were also your people.

27:31.400 --> 27:32.110
Chu.

27:33.310 --> 27:35.770
These horses
are the treasures of Great Yan.

27:35.920 --> 27:37.830
Although they may not look impressive,

27:37.830 --> 27:39.290
they have a fierce temper.

27:39.440 --> 27:42.300
I wonder if the horse tamers of Ximeng
can tame them.

27:43.070 --> 27:44.240
If needed,

27:44.680 --> 27:46.720
I can send a few grooms from Great Yan

27:46.720 --> 27:47.880
over to you.

27:48.480 --> 27:51.940
The horse tamers of Ximeng
all come from hunting backgrounds.

27:52.310 --> 27:54.830
Even fierce beasts in the mountains
are nothing to them,

27:54.830 --> 27:57.590
not to mention a few small

27:57.590 --> 27:59.720
but fierce wild horses from Great Yan.

28:01.350 --> 28:02.400
Not necessarily.

28:03.550 --> 28:05.590
This little white Huolei horse

28:05.590 --> 28:06.720
has a fierce temper.

28:06.920 --> 28:08.070
Even in Great Yan,

28:08.070 --> 28:09.200
no one can tame it.

28:10.110 --> 28:11.240
You must be careful.

28:12.720 --> 28:14.200
Don't let it hurt you.

28:15.200 --> 28:16.270
I'd like to see

28:16.750 --> 28:18.880
just how untamable this wild horse is.

28:27.680 --> 28:28.550
You lied to me?

28:29.510 --> 28:32.040
I picked this white horse
especially for you.

28:32.070 --> 28:34.030
It is gentle and friendly.

29:15.240 --> 29:15.960
Bad news!

29:16.070 --> 29:17.510
Lady Chu went to the horse ranch
with Yan Xun.

29:17.510 --> 29:18.480
And they've been there for half the day.

29:18.480 --> 29:19.030
Even on horseback,

29:19.030 --> 29:20.720
they could have circled Ximengcheng
3 times by now.

29:20.720 --> 29:22.030
Aren't you going to check on them?

29:22.030 --> 29:25.350
The alliance between Ximeng
and Great Yan is a state affair.

29:25.350 --> 29:26.440
Xing is the Queen,

29:26.880 --> 29:28.740
so it's natural for her to do this.

29:30.440 --> 29:31.170
Impressive.

29:31.960 --> 29:32.820
You're so calm.

29:41.350 --> 29:44.510
This is the only place in Ximeng now
where the flowers bloom.

29:44.510 --> 29:45.200
Chu,

29:46.070 --> 29:47.070
I keep dreaming

29:47.830 --> 29:49.630
about what happened 7 years ago,

29:50.200 --> 29:51.860
when my father was still alive

29:54.680 --> 29:56.610
and everything was still as it was.

29:56.960 --> 29:59.960
I returned to Great Yan with you
from Zhenhuangcheng.

30:00.270 --> 30:03.400
We rode Huolei horses together
on Mount Huihui

30:03.640 --> 30:04.920
and bathed in the hot springs.

30:04.920 --> 30:06.650
I even took you to see my mother.

30:06.920 --> 30:07.960
I told her,

30:08.590 --> 30:09.270
"Chu is

30:09.920 --> 30:11.960
the Heir Apparent's wife I chose."

30:12.920 --> 30:14.160
Just as I promised you

30:14.480 --> 30:15.810
back in Qingshan Manor.

30:18.590 --> 30:21.320
As for the alliance
between Great Yan and Ximeng,

30:21.510 --> 30:23.590
the protocol officials are already
drafting a state communiqué.

30:23.590 --> 30:25.450
It will be finalized in a few days.

30:25.640 --> 30:28.300
You will be able to return
to Great Yan very soon.

30:30.550 --> 30:32.030
Are you asking me to leave?

30:33.110 --> 30:33.790
Yan Xun,

30:35.030 --> 30:36.270
we all have to move on.

30:45.680 --> 30:46.720
You are my past,

30:47.550 --> 30:48.680
but also my future.

30:50.750 --> 30:51.810
I want to thank you.

30:52.200 --> 30:53.240
Thank you for accompanying me in hell

30:53.240 --> 30:54.270
for so many years.

30:54.920 --> 30:56.960
Thank you for not abandoning me

30:57.350 --> 30:58.750
in the darkest moments of my life.

30:58.750 --> 31:01.010
Thank you for always standing by my side.

31:05.030 --> 31:06.230
If it weren't for you,

31:07.310 --> 31:08.910
I, Yan Xun, would be nothing,

31:09.240 --> 31:11.680
and I would have died
in the snowy night 7 years ago.

31:11.680 --> 31:14.440
I won't say these things again.

31:15.110 --> 31:17.350
I will make up for my mistakes
with my whole life.

31:17.350 --> 31:19.680
There are some things
we don't need to say.

31:19.750 --> 31:21.610
We should understand each other.

31:21.960 --> 31:23.480
Chu, you belong to me—

31:24.310 --> 31:25.640
and only me.

31:25.960 --> 31:27.030
I will protect you

31:27.790 --> 31:28.790
and take you away.

31:33.310 --> 31:35.160
I took your hand 7 years ago

31:35.590 --> 31:37.510
and never planned to let go.

31:40.640 --> 31:41.270
Chu.

31:43.590 --> 31:44.640
Believe me.

31:48.750 --> 31:49.440
Chu.

31:49.960 --> 31:50.480
Yan Xun.

31:51.590 --> 31:52.310
Right now,

31:54.070 --> 31:56.070
the land of Great Yan is devastated,

31:57.000 --> 31:59.600
and the people of Great Yan
have nothing to eat.

31:59.880 --> 32:01.410
They need you more than I do.

32:02.720 --> 32:04.790
You shouldn't waste your time on me.

32:10.440 --> 32:12.170
I heard the new policy of Ximeng

32:12.480 --> 32:13.940
is welcomed by the people.

32:15.960 --> 32:18.020
My journey of thousands of miles here

32:18.030 --> 32:19.310
was not in vain.

32:27.920 --> 32:28.720
Chu!

32:29.640 --> 32:30.400
Trust me!

32:31.200 --> 32:32.550
I will be a good king!

32:34.310 --> 32:34.920
Yan Xun,

32:36.750 --> 32:37.680
I believe you.

32:51.880 --> 32:53.540
I'm going out to run an errand.

32:58.180 --> 33:00.250
See? He couldn't stay put after all.

33:01.110 --> 33:02.640
You owe me a string of coins.

33:19.030 --> 33:19.960
Why are you here?

33:20.550 --> 33:21.750
The state communiqué

33:22.030 --> 33:24.240
will be delivered
to your residence tomorrow.

33:24.240 --> 33:27.440
King of Great Yan,
you can set your return date in advance.

33:55.310 --> 33:56.110
Young Master.

34:02.030 --> 34:02.720
Young Master,

34:02.720 --> 34:03.310
as you ordered,

34:03.310 --> 34:04.890
I investigated the Faceless God Sect.

34:04.890 --> 34:05.500
[The Faceless God Sect is a recently
emerged organization in Ximeng.]

34:05.310 --> 34:05.880
This organization

34:05.500 --> 34:06.120
[Its leader is said to be a mysterious saintess,
whose true face has never been seen.]

34:05.900 --> 34:07.420
only recently appeared in Ximeng.

34:06.130 --> 34:06.730
[The sect is very mysterious, with followers
spread widely across various countries.]

34:06.730 --> 34:07.340
[Among them, the largest number
is found in Great Yong, where it first appeared.]

34:07.960 --> 34:09.960
It is said the leader is a saintess,

34:10.310 --> 34:12.110
but no one has seen her true face.

34:12.440 --> 34:13.440
Besides Ximeng,

34:14.030 --> 34:15.840
are there believers anywhere else?

34:15.840 --> 34:17.639
There are some in every country.

34:18.110 --> 34:19.370
What about Great Yong?

34:19.670 --> 34:22.929
Great Yong has the most,
and it started there the earliest.

34:23.030 --> 34:26.000
Ximeng has been implementing
the new policy for 4 months.

34:26.000 --> 34:27.000
Great Yong should

34:27.020 --> 34:28.690
have already gathered this information.

34:28.690 --> 34:29.900
You mean...

34:29.960 --> 34:31.489
it's related to Great Yong?

34:42.440 --> 34:43.110
Shiyi,

34:43.320 --> 34:45.760
send someone to Biantang
and give this to He Xiao.

34:45.760 --> 34:46.320
Yes.

35:03.280 --> 35:04.340
This way! This way!

35:16.440 --> 35:17.370
What's going on?

35:18.840 --> 35:19.640
Your Majesty,

35:19.880 --> 35:20.710
Lady Chu.

35:21.320 --> 35:23.150
This place was originally
an abandoned mortuary.

35:23.150 --> 35:25.030
Recently, the Faceless God Sect
has arisen in the city,

35:25.030 --> 35:26.400
so these believers are using this place

35:26.400 --> 35:27.630
as a gathering spot.

35:28.070 --> 35:29.150
But somehow,

35:29.230 --> 35:30.490
it suddenly exploded.

35:30.590 --> 35:31.760
Seventeen people
were killed in the explosion.

35:31.760 --> 35:33.710
Now only a female believer is left alive.

35:33.710 --> 35:36.150
She has already been detained
in the backyard.

35:36.150 --> 35:37.630
I will go see this believer.

35:37.630 --> 35:39.190
I will go check on
the surrounding commoners.

35:39.190 --> 35:40.360
Be careful.

35:58.670 --> 35:59.760
What's your name?

36:01.000 --> 36:02.000
Can you tell me

36:02.760 --> 36:05.290
what exactly happened
during the explosion?

36:11.800 --> 36:14.600
That was divine punishment
from the Faceless God!

36:17.920 --> 36:19.050
Divine punishment?

36:23.000 --> 36:24.320
The people who died

36:24.670 --> 36:27.480
were not true believers
of the Faceless God at all.

36:27.960 --> 36:29.800
Those chosen by the Faceless God

36:29.920 --> 36:31.440
cannot die at all.

36:32.000 --> 36:32.930
What do you mean?

36:34.190 --> 36:38.030
This was the Faceless God
filtering out the true believers.

36:41.730 --> 36:43.190
Filtering out believers?

36:47.600 --> 36:49.690
I am the lucky one

36:51.440 --> 36:53.440
chosen by the god.

36:56.440 --> 36:57.710
Then can you take me

36:58.440 --> 37:00.000
to see your god?

37:04.550 --> 37:06.440
You foolish people

37:06.880 --> 37:08.840
cannot see the Faceless God at all.

37:09.110 --> 37:11.590
The Faceless God will only appear

37:12.320 --> 37:14.030
when she wants to.

37:15.400 --> 37:16.840
Let me out!

37:16.840 --> 37:18.230
I want to see my god!

37:29.480 --> 37:31.280
I just asked the people nearby.

37:31.590 --> 37:32.280
They said

37:32.670 --> 37:34.070
someone told them

37:34.480 --> 37:36.150
the Saintess would appear here today

37:36.150 --> 37:37.280
to worship the Faceless God.

37:37.280 --> 37:39.190
So all the people in the city

37:39.190 --> 37:40.550
who wanted to worship the Saintess

37:40.550 --> 37:41.800
or the Faceless God came here.

37:41.800 --> 37:42.920
But no one expected

37:43.280 --> 37:44.610
an explosion to happen.

37:45.760 --> 37:48.090
What about you? Did you find out anything?

37:48.320 --> 37:51.000
She said she was chosen
by the Faceless God,

37:51.110 --> 37:53.370
and the Faceless God will come to see her.

37:57.070 --> 37:58.960
You may leave.

38:03.670 --> 38:04.230
Minglu.

38:05.550 --> 38:07.510
Stay here and watch her tonight.

38:07.670 --> 38:08.730
Ensure her safety,

38:08.880 --> 38:10.480
but don't let her notice you.

38:10.670 --> 38:11.150
Yes.

38:45.030 --> 38:47.440
Well? Any news?

38:47.540 --> 38:48.940
I followed her all night.

38:49.320 --> 38:51.960
After she returned home yesterday,
she stayed inside and never came out.

38:51.960 --> 38:53.230
And this morning,

38:53.480 --> 38:55.550
she washed up, changed her clothes,
and left the house around 9 AM,

38:55.550 --> 38:58.030
wearing that yellow silk handkerchief
on her wrist

38:58.030 --> 38:59.440
and heading to the South Market.

38:59.440 --> 39:01.040
A yellow silk handkerchief?

39:01.760 --> 39:02.320
Yes.

39:02.920 --> 39:04.360
It's the same yellow silk handkerchief

39:04.360 --> 39:06.070
we previously saw on the wrists

39:06.070 --> 39:07.880
of commoners who follow the Saintess.

39:07.880 --> 39:09.920
I suspect this is their secret signal.

39:09.920 --> 39:11.250
I had Xiao Ran follow her

39:11.360 --> 39:12.890
and hurried back to report.

39:15.360 --> 39:17.020
Tell Meng En to bring a few men.

39:17.280 --> 39:18.410
Let's go take a look.

39:19.280 --> 39:19.840
Okay.

39:25.630 --> 39:26.510
These reports

39:26.670 --> 39:28.400
were gathered from the checkpoints

39:28.400 --> 39:29.110
bordering Ximeng and Great Yan.

39:29.110 --> 39:30.360
They shouldn't be wrong.

39:30.360 --> 39:32.620
Have Yan Xun and the Great Yan delegation

39:32.800 --> 39:34.630
been in Ximengcheng this whole time?

39:34.630 --> 39:35.150
Yes.

39:35.230 --> 39:36.760
Since entering Ximengcheng,

39:36.760 --> 39:38.150
they have been staying at the posthouse
in the western part of the city

39:38.150 --> 39:39.350
and haven't gone out.

39:45.830 --> 39:46.480
Your Majesty,

39:46.480 --> 39:47.340
King Ximeng...

39:53.110 --> 39:55.030
It seems you guessed I would come.

39:58.070 --> 39:59.200
You're just in time.

40:00.630 --> 40:02.560
Come and taste this pheasant soup.

40:04.070 --> 40:07.330
It's a golden pheasant
I brought specially from Great Yan.

40:12.760 --> 40:14.690
It won't taste good if it gets cold.

40:41.030 --> 40:41.800
Bad news!

40:42.320 --> 40:44.520
Lady Chu is now a princess of Great Yong?

40:44.650 --> 40:45.780
All our past ties

40:46.440 --> 40:47.590
are now in vain.

40:47.610 --> 40:49.050
Did it all start

40:49.440 --> 40:50.360
because of you?

40:51.030 --> 40:52.190
If it dies,

40:52.210 --> 40:53.030
I will kill you!

40:53.030 --> 40:55.590
I am you, and you are me.

40:55.650 --> 40:56.730
I am Chu Qiao.

40:57.670 --> 40:59.710
We will be an ordinary couple,

41:00.160 --> 41:01.160
traveling around

41:01.480 --> 41:02.880
and living a free and unrestrained life.
